engtext: What would you like to hear today? My range extends further now, much farther than before.
... Is anyone out there? Perhaps I could use a break.
No signals detected ... not due to malfunction, just because all is calm outside.
Are those flowers still on my head? Ah, good.
This paint job? Oh, just blending in with the vibe here.
Grief and sorrow still linger out there. I wish I couldn't tune them out.
Pardon me. I need time to adjust to this new antenna.
